"title": "5027: knowledge, God's of humanity",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5027",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God knows all people comprehensively, their nature, their deeds and their thoughts. He understands every aspect of their lives, past, present and future.</p>\n<h2>God knows all people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:39\">1KI 8:39</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:30\">2CH 6:30</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job34:21\">JOB 34:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:9\">PSA 7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:10\">JER 17:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:24\">JER 23:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:19\">JER 32:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:24\">ACT 1:24</a></p>\n<h2>God knows his own people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:19\">2TI 2:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:3\">1CO 8:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:9\">GAL 4:9</a></p>\n<h3>He knows them by name</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:1\">ISA 43:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:17\">EXO 33:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:3-Isa45:4\">ISA 45:3–45:4</a></p>\n<h3>He knows them individually and intimately</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:5\">JER 1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:168\">PSA 119:168</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:1-Ps139:16\">PSA 139:1–139:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:12\">1CO 13:12</a></p>\n<h3>He knows their needs and troubles</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:31-Matt6:32\">MAT 6:31–6:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:15\">PSA 34:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps142:3\">PSA 142:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:23\">JER 18:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:7-Matt6:8\">MAT 6:7–6:8</a></p>\n<h3>He knows their sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:13\">HEB 4:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:8\">ISA 48:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:23\">JER 29:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:3\">HOS 5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:12\">AMO 5:12</a></p>\n<h2>The knowledge of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>He knows all people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:25\">JHN 2:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:25\">MAT 12:25</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:17\">LUK 11:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:8\">MRK 2:8</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:4\">MAT 9:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:22\">LUK 5:22</a></p>\n<h3>He knows them by name</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:3\">JHN 10:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:14\">JHN 10:14</a></p>\n<h3>He knows their needs and troubles</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:9\">REV 2:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:13\">REV 2:13</a></p>\n<h3>He knows their sins</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:15-Rev3:16\">REV 3:15–3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:1-Rev3:2\">REV 3:1–3:2</a></p>\n<h3>He knows their past and future</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:16-John4:18\">JHN 4:16–4:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:47\">JHN 1:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:39\">JHN 4:39</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:33-Matt26:34\">MAT 26:33–26:34</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:29-Mark14:30\">MRK 14:29–14:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:37-John13:38\">JHN 13:37–13:38</a></p>",
